  "text": "language\nSkip to main content\nPRO\nPro indicator: A premium offering that requires a paid subscription.\nAmson安生｜數位行銷 x IG變現\nHome\nContacts\nAutomation\nManychat AI\nInbox\n2\nSettings\nMy Profile\nHelp\nSettings\nMain\nGeneral\nNotifications\nTeam Members\nLogs\nDisplay\nBilling\nSubscriptions\nInvoices\nPayment Details\nInbox\nInbox Behavior\nAuto-Assignment\nChannels\nInstagram\nTikTok\nWhatsApp\nMessenger\nSMS\nEmail\nTelegram\nAutomation\nFields\nTags\nConversion Events\nExtensions\nAPI\nApps\nIntegrations\nPayments\nInstalled Templates\nPixel\nIf you or your contacts are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), please be sure to obtain contacts' consent to transferring their data to any 3rd party you are integrating with in order to comply with GDPR.\nCan’t find what you need?\nAsk Us For It\nConnect TikTok Ads Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nBETA\nTikTok Ads\nStep 1\nAuthorize via TikTok. On the next screen, click \"Confirm\" without changing permissions.\nConnect TikTok Ads Account\nOptimize your ad targeting with seamless Manychat integration.\n\nUse clicks in TikTok Instant Messaging Ads as a trigger to start automation in WhatsApp or Facebook Messenger.\nConnect Flodesk Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nBETA\nFlodesk\nConnect Flodesk Account\nThe integration provides you with an ability to save customers data from Manychat to Flodesk. Create a contact if it doesn’t exist in Flodesk already, or update it with Contact’s Custom Fields if it does. Learn more\nConnect Google Sheets Account\nGoogle Sheets\nConnect Google Sheets Account\nThe integration provides you with an ability to save customers data from Manychat bot to Google Sheets. Learn more\nConnect Hotmart Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nHotmart\nConnect Hotmart Account\nHotmart empowers digital entrepreneurs with a leading online platform for selling and promoting digital products.\nConnect ChatGPT Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nChatGPT\nStep 1\nConnect ChatGPT Account\nAPI Secret \nConnect ChatGPT Account\nChatGPT integration enables individuals to accomplish a wide range of tasks. The flexibility and intelligence allow handling various types of requests and offering personalized support.\nConnect Claude Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nBETA\nClaude\nAPI Secret \nConnect Claude Account\nClaude integration enables individuals to accomplish a wide range of tasks. The flexibility and intelligence allow handling various types of requests and offering personalized support.\nConnect DeepSeek Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nBETA\nDeepSeek\nAPI Secret \nConnect DeepSeek Account\nDeepSeek integration enables individuals to accomplish a wide range of tasks. The flexibility and intelligence allow handling various types of requests and offering personalized support.\nConnect Klaviyo Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nBETA\nKlaviyo\nConnect Klaviyo Account\nPublic API Key\nHow to get?\nPrivate API Key\nHow to get?\nConnect Klaviyo Account\nThe integration provides you with an ability to save customers data from Manychat to Klaviyo. Create a contact if it doesn’t exist in Klaviyo already, or update it with Contact’s Custom Fields if it does. Learn more\nConnect ActiveCampaign Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nActiveCampaign\nStep 1\nConnect ActiveCampaign Account\nAPI URL\nHow to get?\nAPI Key\nHow to get?\nConnect ActiveCampaign Account\nActiveCampaign is an email marketing, marketing automation, sales automation, and CRM software platform for small-to-mid-sized businesses. Learn more\nConnect MailChimp Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nMailChimp\nStep 1\nConnect MailChimp Account\nConnect MailChimp Account\nThe integration provides you with an ability to save customers contacts from Manychat to MailChimp. Learn more\nConnect HubSpot Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nHubSpot CRM\nStep 1\nConnect HubSpot Account\nConnect HubSpot Account\nHubSpot CRM is everything you need to organize, track, and nurture your leads and customers. It's 100% free, forever. Learn more\nConnect Kit Account\nUPGRADE\nUpgrade required: This feature requires upgrading your plan to access.\nKit\nStep 1\nConnect Kit Account\nAPI Secret\nMy API Secret\nConnect Kit Account\nKit is an email marketing platform for professional bloggers. You'll need to get API Secret from your Kit account to setup integration.\nLearn more\nExplore Manychat App Store\nImprove the capabilities of your Automations by discovering additional integrations from other Manychat users.\nVisit App Store",
